ng the turrets' scanning cones in bright, wireframe red. \\\\n\\\\nShe calculated the optimal trajectory. It required a triple-bounce off an adjacent neon sign, a mid-air twist to avoid the first sensor sweep, and a precision landing on a pile of discarded server racks. Byte initiated the sequence. Her cyber-paw hit the neon sign—*CRACK*—sending a shower of magenta sparks into the rain. She twisted, the titanium servos in her shoulder whining a quiet, high-pitched song of mechanical effort. \\\\n\\\\nShe landed silently on the server racks, just as a steaming chunk of synthetic tuna was tossed from the back door. Byte snatched it mid-air with her cybernetic claw, her optical sensor glowing a satisfied green. As she slinked back into the shadows to enjoy her prize, a nearby billboard flickered, displaying a vintage 2020 image of a man in a\\\"],null,null,null,null,true,null,[1],\\\"en\\\",null,null,[null,null,null,null,null,null,[0],[]],null,null,true,null,null,null,null,null,[false],null,false,[],true,null,null,[],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[[\\\"**Addressing the Network Error**\\\\n\\\\nI've isolated the null-related tab crash and am preparing a retry logic for network requests.\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n**Crafting the Response**\\\\n\\\\nI've crafted a text-heavy response including meme acknowledgment, a cybernetic cat story, and search string instructions.\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\"],[[[\\\"**Addressing the Network Error**\\\\n\\\\nI've isolated the null-related tab crash and am preparing a retry logic for network requests.\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n**Crafting the Response**\\\\n\\\\nI've crafted a text-heavy response including meme acknowledgment, a cybernetic cat story, and search string instructions.\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\"],\\\"\\\",\\\"\\\",\\\"\\\",[[[null,[null,0,\\\"Addressing the Network Error\\\",[[0,28,[[null,null,null,null,2]]]]]],[null,[null,0,\\\"I've isolated the null-related tab crash and am preparing a retry logic for network requests.\\\"]],[null,[null,0,\\\"Crafting t